column8: I do not believe that my e-waste will be recycled responsibly and I don't want old phones, laptops etc. to end up in west African dumping sites where they are stripped apart, burned, and melted down next to children's homes. E-waste from rich countries is known to be a major source of environmental pollution in the Global South.
